data.description: Check out this adorable home located in Harmony Ridge neighborhood! This cul-de-sac home offers an open floor plan with a gas fireplace in the living room, a half bath, and an island in the updated kitchen with new flooring throughout. Upstairs you will find 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and plenty of storage in the walk-in closets. Enjoy entertaining in a large privacy fenced backyard. Call today for a private showing!
